data.description: HUGE Price Improvement! Serious buyers will not want to miss this amazing opportunity. This exquisite 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom property is a harmonious blend of modern elegance and classic charm. It's been meticulously maintained with hardwood floors flowing seamlessly throughout most of the home, creating an inviting and warm ambiance. The heart of the home is the gourmet kitchen, with recently updated stainless steel appliances, beautiful countertops, breakfast area and ample cabinet space. The first floor also includes a formal living and dining space , laundry room, powder room and two-story entryway. And, have you seen the yard space? The property boasts a vast backyard with endless possibilities. Imagine hosting gatherings on the patio, gardening, or simply enjoying the serene surroundings. Don't sell yourself short- you deserve to have space between you and your neighbors. A storage shed in the backyard adds practicality for your outdoor needs. To top it all off, this home is solar-powered, with electric bills averaging $75 per month (depending on usage). Wow! You can't beat that. Schedule your showing today before it’s gone.
